channel.title: Client is crashing dang it! please help =[
channel.description:
Here's my error, while playing on a server I can click on the map once and I'm fine. BUTTT if I click again it shuts the client and the commant prompt with an error being logged. It doesn't close the client if i click in the inventory area or the chat box, just the places that make my character move. It isn't my client I'm just trying to play the game. Pleaseee help I'm at a loss. Here is what I've tried...
[ul][li]Re-downloading client[/li] [li]Re-downloading java[/li] [li]Re-downloading jre[/li] [li]Re-downloading jdk[/li] [li]I have also tried downloading a source and client to see if it still shuts me down and it does.[/li][/ul]
I've been up all night trying more and more stuff. I thought i had it when i disabled my comp's DEP but no luck.. still looking for help.. I'm running on Vista if that matters at all...Also, it is a 317 client and it is the one made for this server. Here's the error..
